BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 7 (KCNA) -- An agreement on 
cooperation in information service was signed in Vientiane on 
March 31 between the Information Committee of the DPRK and the 
Ministry of Information and Culture of the Lao People's 
Democratic Republic. 
  The agreement was signed by Yi Pong-hui, vice-chairman of 
the 
Information Committee of the DPRK, and Bouasy Chaleunsouk, first 
vice-minister of Information and Culture of Laos. 

